FBIS3-14139 "drnes056_n_94006" FBIS-NES-94-056 Document Type:Daily Report 22 Mar 1994 LEBANON Death Penalty Law Signed for Political Killings NC2203183294 Beirut Voice of Lebanon in Arabic 1715 GMT 22 Mar 94 NC2203183294 Beirut Voice of Lebanon Language: Arabic Article Type:BFN [Text] The president today signed a law instituting the death penalty for first-degree murder and political assassination. He also signed a law amending the grounds for appeal against court verdicts in criminal cases and a law governing the appointment of ordinary and administrative court judges.
